Package: spreads
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python:Depends}, python-usb (>= 1.0.0b1), python-psutil (>= 2.1.1), python-jpegtran (>= 0.5), python-hidapi-cffi (>= 0.2.1), python-roman(>= 2.0.0), python-concurrent.futures (>= 2.1.6)
X-Python-Version: 2.7
Recommends: scantailor, djvubind, pdfbeads, chdkptp
Description: Book digitization workflow suite
 .
 spreads is a tool that aims to streamline your book scanning workflow.
 It takes care of every step: Setting up your capturing devices, handling
 the capturing process, downloading the images to your machine,
 post-processing them and finally assembling a variety of output formats.


